class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Infrastructure\\SymfonyAi\\RunCancellationToken"
type: readonly final class
summary: Provides a mechanism to check if a specific agent run has been cancelled by querying the persistent store. It encapsulates the run identifier and store dependency to determine cancellation status on demand.
